Variable.Name: Adjust
Variable.Comment: Number of seconds per hour (set 0 to indicate 3600)

Variable.Name: HoursRetain
Variable.Comment: Count of hours (updated only every HoursNo hours)

Variable.Name: Alrm
Variable.Comment: Signals that the maximum number of operating hours have been reached

Variable.Name: Q
Variable.Comment: TRUE when CLK rises from FALSE to TRUE. False in other cases

Variable.Name: Du
Variable.Comment: Down/Up, indicate the direction of count

Variable.Name: Enable
Variable.Comment: Enables the update of the output

Variable.Name: MinOnT
Variable.Comment: Minimum on time, in seconds. It starts to count when DevStatus = TRUE

Variable.Name: MinOffT
Variable.Comment: Minimum off time, in seconds. It starts to count when DevStatus = FALSE

Variable.Name: MinOnOnSameT
Variable.Comment: Minimum time between two on, in seconds. It starts when DevStatus = TRUE

Variable.Name: ResSafT
Variable.Comment: Reset all safety times. If fixed to TRUE, the reset works only 1 time. It works on the rising edge.

Variable.Name: FrcdOffByT
Variable.Comment: If true, the device is forced off due to minimum off time or MinOnOnSameT

Variable.Name: FrcdOnByT
Variable.Comment: If true, the device is forced on due to minimum on time

Variable.Name: CntDwnTSaf
Variable.Comment: Remaining time until the device is able to start, in seconds

Variable.Name: CntDwnTMinOn
Variable.Comment: Remaining time until the device is able to stop, in seconds
